#: ../../../release-notes.rst:25
msgid ""
"v0.4.3 introduces the ``@raw_return`` decorator which allows contracts to "
"return bytes directly without ABI-encoding, which enables new proxy contract "
"use cases. The default EVM version has been updated to ``prague``, and "
"several improvements have been made to the Venom optimizer pipeline."
msgstr ""

