msgstr ""

#: ../../../release-notes.rst:64
msgid "Date released: 2025-05-31"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release-notes.rst:66
msgid ""
"v0.4.2 includes a new ``raw_create()`` builtin which allows users to build "
"more generic factories in Vyper. It also moves the ``sqrt()`` builtin to a "
"pure Vyper module, involving a refactor which will allow more stdlib "
"functionality to be written in Vyper in the future."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release-notes.rst:68
msgid ""
"Additionally, Venom has undergone more improvements, including a CSE "
"elimination pass, dead-store elimination pass, as well as moving more items "
"in the calling convention to the stack in the venom pipeline. Benchmark "
"contracts are now typically 5% smaller."
msgstr ""

