#: ../../../release-notes.rst:686
msgid "v0.3.10 (\"Black Adder\")"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release-notes.rst:689
msgid "Date released: 2023-10-04"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release-notes.rst:691
msgid ""
"v0.3.10 is a performance focused release that additionally ships numerous "
"bugfixes. It adds a ``codesize`` optimization mode (`#3493 <https://github."
"com/vyperlang/vyper/pull/3493>`_), adds new vyper-specific ``#pragma`` "
"directives  (`#3493 <https://github.com/vyperlang/vyper/pull/3493>`_), uses "
"Cancun's ``MCOPY`` opcode for some compiler generated code (`#3483 <https://"
"github.com/vyperlang/vyper/pull/3483>`_), and generates selector tables "
"which now feature O(1) performance (`#3496 <https://github.com/vyperlang/"
"vyper/pull/3496>`_)."
msgstr ""

