"github.com/vyperlang/vyper/pull/2064>`_)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release-notes.rst:1370
msgid ""
"``RLPList`` has been removed (VIP `#1866 <https://github.com/vyperlang/vyper/"
"issues/1866>`_)"
msgstr ""

